name: virtuoso-opensource
description: Virtuoso is a high-performance and scalable Multi-Model RDBMS, Data Integration Middleware, Linked Data Deployment, and HTTP Application Server Platform

releases.name: Virtuoso Open Source Edition v7.2.6
releases.body:
OpenLink Software is pleased to announce a new release of Virtuoso Open Source Edition, version 7.2.6

For more details, see the release notes: 
https://github.com/openlink/virtuoso-opensource/blob/stable/7/NEWS.md

Virtuoso Open Source Edition:
Home Page: http://vos.openlinksw.com/
Download Page: http://vos.openlinksw.com/owiki/wiki/VOS/VOSDownload
